        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EInternal%20Workings%20of%20the%20Soviet%20System%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%3Ch1%3EInternal%20Workings%20of%20the%20Soviet%20System%3C%2Fh1%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0AHaving%20come%20to%20power%20in%20October%201917%20by%20means%20of%20a%20coup%20d'%C3%A9tat%2C%20Vladimir%0ALenin%20and%20the%20Bolsheviks%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20years%20struggling%20to%0Amaintain%20their%20rule%20against%20widespread%20popular%20opposition.%20%20They%20had%0Aoverthrown%20the%20provisional%20democratic%20government%20and%20were%20inherently%0Ahostile%20to%20any%20form%20of%20popular%20participation%20in%20politics.%20%20In%20the%20name%0Aof%20the%20revolutionary%20cause%2C%20they%20employed%20ruthless%20methods%20to%20suppress%0Areal%20or%20perceived%20political%20enemies.%20%20The%20small%2C%20elite%20group%20of%0ABolshevik%20revolutionaries%20which%20formed%20the%20core%20of%20the%20newly%0Aestablished%20Communist%20Party%20dictatorship%20ruled%20by%20decree%2C%20enforced%20with%0Aterror.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0AThis%20tradition%20of%20tight%20centralization%2C%20with%20decision-making%0Aconcentrated%20at%20the%20highest%20party%20levels%2C%20reached%20new%20dimensions%20under%0AJoseph%20Stalin.%20%20As%20many%20of%20these%20archival%20documents%20show%2C%20there%20was%0Alittle%20input%20from%20below.%20%20The%20party%20elite%20determined%20the%20goals%20of%20the%0Astate%20and%20the%20means%20of%20achieving%20them%20in%20almost%20complete%20isolation%20from%0Athe%20people.%20%20They%20believed%20that%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20individual%20were%20to%0Abe%20sacrificed%20to%20those%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20was%20advancing%20a%20sacred%0Asocial%20task.%20%20Stalin's%20%22revolution%20from%20above%22%20sought%20to%20build%0Asocialism%20by%20means%20of%20forced%20collectivization%20and%20industrialization%2C%0Aprograms%20that%20entailed%20tremendous%20human%20suffering%20and%20loss%20of%20life.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0AAlthough%20this%20tragic%20episode%20in%20Soviet%20history%20at%20least%20had%20some%0Aeconomic%20purpose%2C%20the%20police%20terror%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20party%20and%20the%0Apopulation%20in%20the%201930s%2C%20in%20which%20millions%20of%20innocent%20people%20perished%2C%0Ahad%20no%20rationale%20beyond%20assuring%20Stalin's%20absolute%20dominance.%20%20By%20the%0Atime%20the%20Great%20Terror%20ended%2C%20Stalin%20had%20subjected%20all%20aspects%20of%20Soviet%0Asociety%20to%20strict%20party-state%20control%2C%20not%20tolerating%20even%20the%0Aslightest%20expression%20of%20local%20initiative%2C%20let%20alone%20political%0Aunorthodoxy.%20%20The%20Stalinist%20leadership%20felt%20especially%20threatened%20by%0Athe%20intelligentsia%2C%20whose%20creative%20efforts%20were%20thwarted%20through%20the%0Astrictest%20censorship%3B%20by%20religious%20groups%2C%20who%20were%20persecuted%20and%0Adriven%20underground%3B%20and%20by%20non-Russian%20nationalities%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%0Adeported%20en%20masse%20to%20Siberia%20during%20World%20War%20II%20because%20Stalin%0Aquestioned%20their%20loyalty.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0AAlthough%20Stalin's%20successors%20also%20persecuted%20writers%20and%20dissidents%2C%0Athey%20used%20police%20terror%20more%20sparingly%20to%20coerce%20the%20population%2C%20and%0Athey%20sought%20to%20gain%20some%20popular%20support%20by%20relaxing%20political%20controls%0Aand%20introducing%20economic%20incentives.%20Nonetheless%2C%20strict%20centralization%0Acontinued%20and%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20economic%20decline%2C%20inefficiency%2C%20and%0Aapathy%20that%20characterized%20the%201970s%20and%201980s%2C%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%0AChernobyl'%20nuclear%20disaster.%20%20Mikhail%20Gorbachev's%20program%20of%0Aperestroika%20was%20a%20reaction%20to%20this%20situation%2C%20but%20its%20success%20was%0Alimited%20by%20his%20reluctance%20to%20abolish%20the%20bastions%20of%20Soviet%20power--the%0Aparty%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20the%20centralized%20economic%20system--until%20he%20was%0Aforced%20to%20do%20so%20after%20the%20attempted%20coup%20in%20August%201991.%20%20By%20that%20time%2C%0Ahowever%2C%20it%20was%20too%20late%20to%20hold%20either%20the%20Communist%20leadership%20or%20the%0ASoviet%20Union%20together.%20%20After%20seventy-four%20years%20of%20existence%2C%20the%0ASoviet%20system%20crumbled.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cimg%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22repress.html%22%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlease%20follow%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22repress.html%22%3Eguided%20tour%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20have%20a%20look%20at%20one%20of%0Athese%20showcases%3A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22repress.html%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22repress.html%22%3ERepression%20and%20Terror%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22secret.html%22%3ESecret%20Police%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22gulag.html%22%3EThe%20Gulag%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22collect.html%22%3ECollectivization%20and%20Industrialization%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22anti_rel.html%22%3EAnti-Religious%20Campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22attack.html%22%3EAttacks%20on%20Intelligentsia%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22famine.html%22%3EUkrainian%20Famine%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22deport.html%22%3EDeportations%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22jac.html%22%3EJewish%20Antifascist%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22chernobyl.html%22%3EChernobyl'%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22perest.html%22%3EPerestroika%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%0AWhen%20you%20have%20seen%20them%20all%20you%20should%20walk%20back%20to%20the%20%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22entrance.html%23tour%22%3Eentrance%20hall%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2F